                "html": "<ul class=\"trust-row\" role=\"list\" data-reveal=\"up\">\n  <li class=\"trust-row__item\"><span class=\"check\" aria-hidden=\"true\">&#10003;</span>Recognized as a Leader by Gartner&reg; Magic Quadrant&trade;</li>\n  <li class=\"trust-row__item\"><span class=\"check\" aria-hidden=\"true\">&#10003;</span>SOC 2 Type II &amp; ISO 27001 Certified</li>\n  <li class=\"trust-row__item\"><span class=\"check\" aria-hidden=\"true\">&#10003;</span>Live in 250+ enterprises across 100 countries</li>\n</ul>"
